# Rewind with speed and pause loop style demo
Output examples/svgs/loop-style/loop-style-rewind.svg

Set FontSize 14
Set Theme pandaSyntax
Set Title "Rewind (10x speed)"
Set LoopStyle rewind
Set RewindSpeed 10
Set LoopPause 1500

Type "echo 'Hello world'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Type "echo 'Fast rewind then pause...'"
Sleep 1s
